    <div class="eyebrow" style="margin-bottom:8px;">The checklist</div>
    <h2 class="h2" style="margin-bottom:8px;">The monthly bookkeeping checklist.</h2>
    <p style="font-size:15px;color:var(--color-ink-mute);margin:0 0 8px;">Seven steps, in order. Run them the same way every month &mdash; if you hit a step the file won&rsquo;t pass, like an account that won&rsquo;t reconcile, stop and get the file reviewed before it compounds.</p>
