      <p>The value of a monthly close is consistency &mdash; the same seven steps, the same way, every month, so the books never fall behind and the reports are always current. A Certified QuickBooks ProAdvisor with active Online and Desktop certifications runs exactly this checklist against a written scope: every transaction coded, every account reconciled, AR and AP cleared, adjustments recorded, the statements reviewed, payroll and sales-tax liabilities verified, and the period locked. If the file is behind first, we bring it current, then keep it current. Independent firm &mdash; not Intuit, and not Intuit&rsquo;s software support; an Intuit account, login, or billing matter stays with Intuit.</p>
